@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### REQ 101: Get all courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list

### REQ 102: Search course by ID (Use correct ID from create response if checking manually, here assuming 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/search/id?courseId=999

### REQ 103: Get promoted courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/promote

### REQ 104: Create a course with specific ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "course_id": 999,
    "title": "Custom ID Course",
    "description": "Course with specific ID",
    "duration": 60,
    "lecturer": "Dr. Specific",
    "category": "Other",
    "promote": false,
    "course_image": "custom.jpg"
}

### REQ 105: Update course (Assumes course_id 1)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/course/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "course_id": 999,
    "promote": false,
    "description": "Updated Description"
}

### REQ 106: Delete course
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/course/delete?courseId=999
